"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-other-sport-imane-khelif-olympic-gold-medal-gender-scandal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"WATCH NOW: ''It is just unfair!'\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 32, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Martin Daubney erupts after activist defends Imane Khelif - 'My children were in tears!'\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999940372954789, \"rank\": 5.961447306694242e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ByJack Otway,  Published: 01/08/2025  Today marks a year since the boxer beat Angela Carini, who was reduced to tears  A year ago today, Imane Khelif was thrust into the spotlight after beating Angela Carini at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"score\": 0.9923857540259575, \"rank\": 0.007672664181437475, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 260, \"end\": 272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini lasted just 46 seconds against her Algerian opponent, with the boxer reduced to tears after being left bloodied and bruised in the French capital.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999974615343876, \"rank\": 2.5384721787357273e-06, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9998237639492366, \"rank\": 0.00014200253381433886, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991905320567663, \"rank\": 0.0007684648197091735, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif had been permitted to compete at the Olympics despite previously being disqualified from the women's world championships, having failed two gender eligibility tests.The fighter, now 26, smacked Carini's chinstrap - with a second punch then seeing blood spray onto the Italian's shorts.Imane Khelif won gold at the Paris Olympics last summer amid gender controversy|GETTYAfter just 46 seconds, Carini had had enough.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999974615343876, \"rank\": 2.5384721787357273e-06, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9818926901750729, \"rank\": 0.014307670889937917, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999974615343876, \"rank\": 2.5384721787357273e-06, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterwards, she said: \\\"I have never felt a punch like this.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got into the ring to fight.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not give up, but one punch hurt too much and so I said enough.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going out with my head held high.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the second punch, after years of experience, I felt a strong pain in the nose.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said enough, because I did not want.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not finish the fight after the punch to the nose.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was better to put an end to it.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She added: \\\"Even if they had said that we would not fight, I would never have accepted it.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a warrior's mentality.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I did not manage.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt too much pain on my nose.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said enough.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a defeat for me - for me if you go in the ring you have already won, regardless of everything else.JUST IN:Harry Redknapp's \\u00a35million Dorset home BURGLED as wife Sandra's jewellery targeted\\\"I am not here to judge.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"score\": 0.9695553924689311, \"rank\": 0.018423832802238502, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not up to me to say if it's fair or not fair.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just did my job.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I managed to leave with my head held high.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a mature woman; when I feel I cannot continue, its not giving in, it's having the dignity to say enough.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was convinced I would win, I was concentrated, serene.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But these punches to the nose hurt, I said enough.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Khelif proceeded to win gold at the Olympics, despite the controversy over whether the Algerian should be competing or not.And over the past year, there have been numerous calls for the 26-year-old to return the gold medal that was secured in Paris last year.READ MORE:Tom Brady blasts 'work ethic' of Wayne Rooney as details emerge about nightmare time at BirminghamImane Khelif beat Angela Carini a year ago today at the Paris Olympics|GettyIBA president Umar Kremlev, speaking earlier this summer, condemned the IOC for letting Khelif compete at the Games.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9998237639492366, \"rank\": 0.00014200253381433886, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991268851, \"rank\": 8.731184840933733e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2380, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.632474204148729e-29, \"text\": \"Tom Brady\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\"}, {\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayne_Rooney\", \"score\": 0.9999998813023082, \"rank\": 1.1869786115502504e-07, \"text\": \"Rooney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayne_Rooney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayne_Rooney\"}, {\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999999993460733, \"rank\": 6.541276492181481e-10, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}, {\"begin\": 2626, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC is not fighting for the fairness in sport,\\\" he told the Daily Mail.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8119815321541048e-12, \"text\": \"Daily Mail\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC is giving away medals based on their political interests.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2751, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif should be made to return the Olympic medal from Paris.\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2813, \"end\": 2825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991268851, \"rank\": 8.731184840933733e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Kremlev then elaborated on the gender tests which Khelif reportedly failed two years ago.He continued: \\\"The first test was carried out during the 2022 World Championships, after we noticed some suspicious, suspicious moments.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We decided to test a group of athletes, not just one or two.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of the results came back, let us say, abnormal.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the first time we had encountered a situation like this, so we felt it was necessary to conduct a second round of testing to be absolutely sure before making such a serious decision.\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That second test was done in 2023 and confirmed the same findings as the first.\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both tests showed XY chromosomes.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That does not meet the eligibility requirements for female boxing.\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After that, the athletes were disqualified, and of course, we informed the IOC about the situation.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3666, \"end\": 3669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, Khelif will not be forced to give back last year's gold - despite the controversy the boxer's participation in the competition caused.LATEST SPORTS NEWS:Chloe Kelly makes heartbreaking admission just days after firing England to Euro 2025 gloryStuart Pearce makes stance clear on Sarina Wiegman managing in the Premier League after Lionesses successTrans darts star releases emotional statement after being banned from playing against womenImane Khelif was permitted to compete at the Paris Olympics by the IOC due to their gender eligibility rules|Imane KhelifDoraine Lambelet Coleman, a Thomas L. Perkins Distinguished Professor of Laws at Duke Law School, explained to Newsweek in June: \\\"The IOC would not revoke medals won by athletes who were eligible according to the rules it set for the boxing competition in Paris.\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 4523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3853, \"end\": 3864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Kelly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chloe Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Kelly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Kelly\"}, {\"begin\": 3918, \"end\": 3925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9992874389958515, \"rank\": 0.0007122132093804632, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3980, \"end\": 3994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarina_Wiegman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarina Wiegman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarina_Wiegman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarina_Wiegman\"}, {\"begin\": 4011, \"end\": 4025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.047798498781772e-15, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}, {\"begin\": 4207, \"end\": 4210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4278, \"end\": 4285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\", \"score\": 0.9973627486983411, \"rank\": 0.0022649891357552584, \"text\": \"Coleman\", \"types\": [\"