"sentence\": \"\\\"We understand that there'll be differences depending on the sport\\u2026 but it was very clear from the members that we have to protect the female category, first and foremost to ensure fairness,\\\" said the 41-year-old.\", \"from\": 9985, \"to\": 10198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kirsty Coventry has insisted the IOC will protect the female category going forward but will not be taking any retrospective action  \\\"But we need to do that with a scientific approach and the inclusion of the international federations who have already done a lot of work in this area.\\\"\", \"from\": 10200, \"to\": 10485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10200, \"end\": 10215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirsty Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\"}, {\"begin\": 10233, \"end\": 10236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coventry also insisted the IOC would not be taking Khelif's medal away, too.\", \"from\": 10487, \"to\": 10563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10514, \"end\": 10517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9505462907199843e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"We are not going to be doing anything retrospectively.\", \"from\": 10565, \"to\": 10631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to be looking forward.\", \"from\": 10632, \"to\": 10667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the members [it] was 'what are we learning from the past, and how are we going to leverage that and move that forward to the future?'\\\"\", \"from\": 10668, \"to\": 10807, \"entities\": []}]}"